This icy whip deals extra cold damage to any target it hits. Creatures you hit with this whip that are not immune to cold suffer slowed movement speed for 5-10 seconds (as the spell [[ray of frost]]).

Once you attune yourself to this weapon, its normally frigid handle feels warm to the touch.